{"tid":1399333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要夾實旺角啲商場，免得又有吳三桂引清兵入關","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:05:49.000Z","uid":295300,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cdfca0e4252cf023258209188d947d532563f272","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"基於實在有太多保安唔用腦（或本身藍絲）引清兵入關，<br />\n今日我哋係需要夾實旺角啲商場，確保佢地嘅前線保安知道商場係私人地方，<br />\n喺冇搜查令嘅情況下，係唔可以亂畀警察入去執勤，<br />\n以免馬鞍山同新城市嘅情況再現<br />\n<br />\n以下係旺角主要商場嘅 Facebook ：<br />\n朗豪坊 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/langhamplacemall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flanghamplacemall%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=3e7f278c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/langhamplacemall/</a><br />\nT.O.P  - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/topmongkok/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftopmongkok%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=d422c838\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/topmongkok/</a><br />\n雅蘭中心 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/grandplazahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgrandplazahk%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=173347f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/grandplazahk/</a><br />\n新之城 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/newtownmall.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnewtownmall.hk%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=675f0b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/newtownmall.hk/</a><br />\n旺角中心 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/argylecentremall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fargylecentremall%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7322d256\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/argylecentremall/</a><br />\n<br />\n留言 Template： 本人今日一家大少會到貴 商場食飯行街，知道旺角會有遊行，想請問貴 商場前線嘅保安同客服人員係咪清楚知道商場係私人地方，警員冇搜令係不能隨便入內？本人好關心個人同家人嘅安全，請回覆解疑。唔該晒。<br />\n<br />\n（大家自由發揮啦）<br />\n<br />\n附加資料 - 警員點先可以入商場<br />\n<br />\n// 記者另翻查《警察通例》，當中第44章規定，警員在未獲得合法授權，或獲得擁有人或佔用人的同意，不得進入任何處所搜查，即使於獲得擁有人或佔用人的同意進入後，如該擁有人或佔用人其後不同意，警員亦須立即離開。惟若是作出拘捕則另當別論，《警隊條例》第50條列明，如警員有理由相信任何須予逮捕的人已進入或置身在某處，則管理該處的人在警員提出要求時須容許其自由進入該處。大律師何旳匡解釋，即使商場地契無列明警員可入內執法，惟根據警例，警員可以拘捕疑犯為由進入私人地方，只是進入有關地方前需通知場地佔用人，「若業主不准警方進入，警方都有權撞門、爆門、打破窗門進入」。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190717/s00001/1563301379081/6商場地契准警執法-包括太古新城市\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563301379081%2F6%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=d186c4d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563301379081%2F6%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&h=51920c18\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190717/s00001/1563301379081/6商場地契准警執法-包括太古新城市</a>"},{"pid":"de3ff5983070bd6c5962717e682d33a0f3d89108","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ac44f71aecace65208a1de110e1dbfeeb563307a","tid":1399333,"uid":3571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"619e95ff80b218856fb9db15136d594c2c7192fa","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"76112c3b3dda7a99da68b4c213a43b76053f8e19","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac44f71ae