333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c367080e06a7c4c1612a24ca0b4a78c66314c9","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38145aeb4e3c495337c5612eb023bf10d32f84b","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2045d4dad06d45d722574564b1b49dd06fee4042","tid":1399333,"uid":55193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"朗豪坊有好幾個都退休警犬"},{"pid":"1637ebf942794fe8352758ee16f4d0dd5f6ac27e","tid":1399333,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，4方配合。<br />\n- 可以短暫防守，不長期守，如果見到狗察就快完成佈防，就要立即換街道。<br />\n- 如果有信心反擊畜龍或水車，可以大反擊。如果無辦法打倒，就不要等待畜龍突擊先識退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，不留戀一個戰線地方，盡量聽同伴意見，不要被捕。"},{"pid":"2fc63c07eed70e89feade4d222828ef4e02e4cdc","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68db8686ed3c70ebc561d8276461cfd21186e60","tid":1399333,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}